<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_156_r1l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> . Von des tages <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>frankf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / wie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> die <expan>fürſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l3">do <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan> ſcheıden <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / vnd was ew <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſölıche<ex>n</ex></expan> lewffen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l4">füglıch wer cʒe <expan>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr davon / als vil ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l5">füglıch dunk / an <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe bey <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>gege<ex>n</ex>w<ex>er</ex>tıge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l6">wöllet / Dar an beweiſt Jr vns <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> die vvir </ab>
