<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>, von des tages <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        czü <expan>Frankf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, wie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> die
                                <expan>fürst<ex>e</ex>n</expan> do <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan> scheiden <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> und
                        was ew <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>söliche<ex>n</ex></expan> lewffen füglich wer cze
                                <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir davon, als vil ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> füglich dunk, an
                                <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe bey
                            <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>gege<ex>n</ex>w<ex>er</ex>tige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, dar an beweist ir uns
                                <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>
<expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, die wir allczeit
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>u<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> wöllen.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
